{"tid":1840354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"袁國勇教授篇論文（懶人包）","createTime":"2020-01-24T19:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T12:10:50.000Z","uid":254022,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fb04a1860853ba5b9264dd74d3b4eae160e401af","tid":1840354,"uid":254022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:49:13.000Z","msg":"篇文刊載係Lancet，其中一本醫學權威期刊<br />\nA familial cluster of pneumonia associated with the 2019 novel coronavirus indicating person-to-person transmission: a study of a family cluster (Chan et al., 2020) <br />\n<br />\n背景：6位病人入面，5位係12月29至1月4到武漢其中一間醫院探病；最後1位比佢地係深圳傳染，1月10-11日到港大深圳醫院求診 （可想而知病毒一早散播晒）<br />\n<br />\n重點：<br />\n1. WARS 基因排序跟係蝙蝠上搵到既 2003 SARS cornaviruses 最為接近 (78% nucleotide identity)，但WARS比SARS勁 （The attack rate is rather high）<br />\n2. 病徵係唔specific <br />\n*唔一定咳先係，初期肚瀉都可能係病徵（同部分SARS同MARS病人相同）<br />\n*無病徵係有可能（佢交篇文果陣應該香港未公佈）<br />\n3. 無證據顯示尿同屎有病毒隱藏（no viral shedding in urine and faeces in these six patients）<br />\n4. WARS 係人傳人方面係非常有效率，唔再做好infection control，相信好快會係另一個super-spreading events <br />\n5. 病毒一早散播晒 (Infected Chinese travellers from Wuhan being detected in other geographical regions)<br />\n6. 係流行病早期階段應該採取更加警惕既infection control<br />\n*而我地香港既第一線係訓緊覺唔做野<br />\n<br />\n無統一指標去分辦感染者，所以根本就係有必要封口岸<br />\nP.S. WARS係好易係屋企，醫院同城市之間傳播<br />\n所以唔該大家戴口罩，如果拜年有鄰國親戚或者最近番過鄰國既人，麻煩唔好除口罩"},{"pid":"1220b06393ac73c480079332ccb072cf14a298a4","tid":1840354,"uid":254022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:49:54.000Z","msg":"戴口罩 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a12cbdd5c8dfa999277870a46592a1baf9844220","tid":1840354,"uid":254022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:50:04.000Z","msg":"戴口罩 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"e5b919734bc30d7b61679e16b7aa23d57c9dab69","tid":1840354,"uid":254022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:51:50.000Z","msg":"戴口罩 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8f022d432c545474552f3372387bbef60d56ef22","tid":1840354,"uid":254022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:52:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩唔好除口罩</span></span>"},{"pid":"3590a30db91b5f2e5d2b7d41c1b1cffb463878cc","tid":1840354,"uid":5416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:52:17.000Z","msg":"有無全文睇吓"},{"pid":"4061b51e95ba001399c85e9a31d292c4f485823a","tid":1840354,"uid":254022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3590a30db91b5f2e5d2b7d41c1b1cffb463878cc","tid":1840354,"uid":5416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:52:17.000Z","msg":"有無全文睇吓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:52:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flancet%2Farticle%2FPIIS0140-6736%2820&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=fde96df1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(20</a>)30154-9/fulltext"},{"pid":"b21379057f3f93b05d754294dcd86e02b5640a38","tid":1840354,"uid":237015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:53:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b37ef3effe9f3ae0ed7dde35fac09ae24622d695","tid":1840354,"uid":254022,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:53:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果拜年有鄰國親戚或者最近番過鄰國既人，麻煩唔好除口罩</span>"},{"pid":"6e09f87db9d4e9501d76dbb66e398e6fdced3195","tid":1840354,"uid":2110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:54:54.000Z","msg":"封關<br />\n不讓香港成為另一個疫區<br />\n不給國家添麻煩<br />\n不給國家做成負擔<br />\n才是最大的愛國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將上面段說話廣傳/整成長輩圖，我地要借助藍絲既愛國之心，先可以更容易保衛香港"},{"pid":"2bb6149fd5637077ece18a1ff291068385ec43f7","tid":1840354,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:55:02.000Z","msg":"香港人醒啦 